{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781763204580,"sessionID":"ses_126a3e098ffexlbbiPvr4M06CK","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_T3K6GXo4B06ocoH9WmpbmEoP","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/B-rest-of-002\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-7\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55r2-b-7-1781761339355-o7qylx\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.maxIterations: 1\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-7 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-b-7. Do not touch any path outside /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research