{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763339347,"sessionID":"ses_126a3e098ffexlbbiPvr4M06CK","part":{"id":"prt_ed95edfe3001FcTs6EzluDYqst","messageID":"msg_ed95ed51a001S3xNq8v6rV32tT","sessionID":"ses_126a3e098ffexlbbiPvr4M06CK","type":"text","text":"Retention appears intentionally tombstone-aware and revalidates inside the delete transaction, so I’m checking the underlying index delete path and then causal/write lifecycle for orphaning risks.","time":{"start":1781763334115,"end":1781763339343},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0e25536fa0a2a6e5016a338d0618d0819187aafbb89b0de48b","phase":"commentary"}}}}
