{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763369381,"sessionID":"ses_126a3e098ffexlbbiPvr4M06CK","part":{"id":"prt_ed95f578a001nyH1F3EWZC1L0q","messageID":"msg_ed95f4037001ddVMOi7HLOCXJz","sessionID":"ses_126a3e098ffexlbbiPvr4M06CK","type":"text","text":"No orphaning issue so far: `delete_memory_from_database` wraps vector, ancillary, causal sweep, embedding cache, and `memory_index` delete in one transaction. I’m checking the save/update path next because that is the highest-risk writer.","time":{"start":1781763364746,"end":1781763369377},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_03552064e9631f38016a338d24b37c8191b8b58acc73c32448","phase":"commentary"}}}}
